definitions: the state of a disease not yet manifesting the usual symptoms

definitions: the delay before a transfer of data begins following an instruction for its transfer

examples.text: poor performance due to network latency
subscribers can expect some latency time when issuing a request
there are several ways to minimize rotational latencies

shortDefinitions: delay before transfer of data begins
